🛠️ Technologies Used
Python 🐍
Pandas & NumPy
Matplotlib & Seaborn
⚙️ Project Workflow
1. Data Cleaning
Converted date_added to datetime
Filled missing values (director, cast, country)
Removed inconsistencies
2. Feature Engineering
Extracted:
year_added
release_decade
Created:
is_movie (binary classification)
Analyzed country popularity
3. Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
Pie chart: Movies vs TV shows
